{"tid":1550743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講左咁耐左膠擋人賣隊友既問題","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T00:27:31.000Z","uid":164705,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43292dfa9169399225500a05f7702c8770195e54","tid":1550743,"uid":164705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係d狗扮左膠，一有事又護人地走？<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始幫黑社會擋拳既左膠一概要出示解鎖手機等資料，如果唔係就當你地係狗扮左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 打埋一份"},{"pid":"bbd1214105262ecebece42200511d7ffe4649489","tid":1550743,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2b3cb7cb47f86a1641951563ff6b7fef3e7d748b","tid":1550743,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17aeec14463413f9d1b0a6b8f9046a9014f72b9e","tid":1550743,"uid":40628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻人嗰啲藍絲扮架，支持送中，支持警察架"},{"pid":"d7a03efca2b5ec16688f93a399a6f708245170d1","tid":1550743,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912ff91a15316a4e436e230008836d8a790ff27e","tid":1550743,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"不要說 「 左膠 」<br />\n<br />\n試着說 「 藍絲臥底 」"},{"pid":"a9ce2876bb89285f74718d99fecb5f5b7b41650e","tid":1550743,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43292dfa9169399225500a05f7702c8770195e54","tid":1550743,"uid":164705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係d狗扮左膠，一有事又護人地走？<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始幫黑社會擋拳既左膠一概要出示解鎖手機等資料，如果唔係就當你地係狗扮左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 打埋一份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f30ae23009a0c997889dfba5069bd81eb54430b","tid":1550743,"uid":124091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"私了埋佢地啦！次撚次都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n荃灣個手足仲有排休養啊你地記唔撚記得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621073843a700daea7f6398ba26f451648e679a8","tid":1550743,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:44:39.000Z"